  <description>
    <p>
    Audok is a simple linux folder based music player with streamripper and converter support.
    Audok is written in python3, the graphical user interface uses gtk.
    Audok is a free software under the GPL license.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>play mp3,wav,flac files</li>
      <li>youtube-dl support (mp3 downloader)</li>
      <li>streamripper support</li>
      <li>record wav files</li>
      <li>covert wav,ts,flac,mp4 to mp3</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
